Investigation_PRJNA280743.name: Tipton et al., Diversity, cellular origin and autoreactivity of antibody-secreting cell population expansions in acute systemic lupus erythematosus

StudyArm_Control (Healthy).name: Control (Healthy)
StudyArm_Control (Healthy).inclusion_criteria: 8 healthy subjects, 4 with trivalent influenza vaccination and 4 with tetanus vaccination, 8 SLE patients experiecing acute flares.
